But here before we goe any further to searche in this matter and to wade (as it were) to searche and trie oute (as we maie) the trueth therof in the scripture, it shall do well by the way to knowe, whether they that thus make aunswere and solution to the former principall question, doe take awaye simplye and absolutlye the presence of Christes bodie and bloud, from the sacrament ordeined by Christ, and duely ministred according to his holye ordi- nance, and institution of the same.
